Oh, sorry to hear that.

00:15:17.340 --> 00:15:18.340
Thank you.

00:15:18.340 --> 00:15:19.340
Thank you.

00:15:19.340 --> 00:15:22.340
So my mom and I was with my brother.

00:15:22.340 --> 00:15:25.340
But at that time, the congregation helped us a lot to progress

00:15:25.340 --> 00:15:26.340
and get baptized.

00:15:26.340 --> 00:15:30.340
So I made it a goal to strengthen my relationship with Jehovah.

00:15:30.340 --> 00:15:32.340
Then at the right moment of my life,

00:15:32.340 --> 00:15:35.340
I made Andreina and eventually we got married.

00:15:35.340 --> 00:15:37.340
What happens next with you, too?

00:15:37.340 --> 00:15:39.340
Now that you're married.

00:15:39.340 --> 00:15:42.340
So when we got married, we were not regular pioneers.

00:15:42.340 --> 00:15:44.340
