00:25:30.339 --> 00:25:33.339
We just feel so grateful since the beginning,

00:25:33.339 --> 00:25:37.339
also the way that our both of our families supported us,

00:25:37.339 --> 00:25:43.339
also the examples of brothers like that couple, Jean and Carla Papino,

00:25:43.339 --> 00:25:44.339
everything.

00:25:44.339 --> 00:25:46.339
We've seen how Jehovah has guided us,

00:25:46.339 --> 00:25:51.339
how he has given us blessings that we never foresaw coming.

00:25:52.339 --> 00:25:57.339
And all these new chapters that we added into our lives,

00:25:57.339 --> 00:25:59.339
we are very happy for that.

00:25:59.339 --> 00:26:04.339
Yes, we're very, very grateful to all those,

00:26:04.339 --> 00:26:07.339
the brothers and sisters that helped us along the way.

00:26:07.339 --> 00:26:11.339
And like my wife is saying it, we don't regret it at all.

